{
  "1859290": {
    "name": "挖矿大亨模拟器 Crypto Miner Tycoon Simulator",
    "steam_appid": 1859290,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859290/extras/ea0e633dbdab96e28f3c0fefc64552a2.poster.avif?t=1770129395\" width=616 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859290/extras/ea0e633dbdab96e28f3c0fefc64552a2.webm?t=1770129395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859290/extras/ea0e633dbdab96e28f3c0fefc64552a2.mp4?t=1770129395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《挖矿大亨模拟器》完整模拟了加密货币挖矿产业，游戏内包含多个剧本。在第一个剧本中，你将化身一名痴迷数字货币的土豪父亲的孩子。他不是很懂这方面的技术，所以他给了你一点钱，让你尝试开展自己的挖矿业务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重温挖矿辉煌史</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在2010年自己的卧室中开始游戏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 历史精准货币汇率</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 体验包括解锁新硬件在内的各类事件</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 加速游戏时间至28800x倍</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859290/extras/ea0e633dbdab96e28f3c0fefc64552a2.poster.avif?t=1770129395\" width=616 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859290/extras/ea0e633dbdab96e28f3c0fefc64552a2.webm?t=1770129395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859290/extras/ea0e633dbdab96e28f3c0fefc64552a2.mp4?t=1770129395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中采用真实的货币价格，但你的行动可以改变历史进程。举个例子，你可以通过建立公关部来影响媒体舆论，或炒作部分货币的升降。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >搭建矿机</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 使用电脑部件组装挖矿设备</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 安装软件</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 利用机架规划空间和热量</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 更换损坏及过时部件</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >专为此游戏编写了一个特制的C++游戏引擎，以支持每个设施中的100000个挖矿单元。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859290/extras/8d0a29ea5112c9245069012bc560d7f4.poster.avif?t=1770129395\" width=616 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859290/extras/8d0a29ea5112c9245069012bc560d7f4.webm?t=1770129395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859290/extras/8d0a29ea5112c9245069012bc560d7f4.mp4?t=1770129395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挖掘加密货币</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 经历CPU、GPU、FPGA和ASIC挖矿时代</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 挖掘比特币、以太币以及更多其他货币……</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 真实全网算力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 管理电力、热量、噪音和灰尘</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搭建具有冷却系统且灰尘等级低的数据中心。降低研究实验室的噪音。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >管理你的公司</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 购买或租用新的办公室</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 聘用人员</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 安排工作班次和任务优先级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 支付月度账单</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以通过升级你的管理技能或雇佣专业管理者解锁加班。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >研究</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 拓展员工技能</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 建立科研实验室</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在竞争开始前捷足先登发现新的技术</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 创建你自己的的加密货币并启动区块链众筹</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个游戏剧本都有与故事相关的特殊研究目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自定义</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 自定义你的角色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 制定员工着装要求</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 使用任意货币 (CNY, $, GBP, EUR, RUB…)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 支持英制与公制系统</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你还在等什么？10年前才是挖矿的最佳时期。</p>",
